Navitia,io,is,an,API,that,helps,people,access,and,use,public,transportation,data,It,provides,services,for,performing,journey,computations,getting,line,schedules,finding,next,departures,and,discovering,isochrones,Isochrones,are,locations,that,can,be,reached,in,the,same,amount,of,time,from,a,person,s,starting,point,This,part,of,the,API,could,for,example,be,used,to,discover,which,stations,could,be,reached,within,the,next,minutes,The,street,network,used,by,navitia,io,is,extracted,from,OpenStreetMap,and,all,of,the,public,transport,data,comes,from,networks,that,provide,their,timetables,as,open,data